# Portfolio Design System — Cursor Rules

This file is the single source of truth for how to edit and extend this project. The design system overrides conventional patterns for creative portfolios. Apply these rules exactly.

---

## 1. Stack & File Structure

- **Stack**: React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS (or CSS Modules)
- **Tokens**: `src/tokens/` — TypeScript constants for colors, spacing, typography, motion, layout
- **Atomic components**: `src/components/ui/` — Button, Card, Input, etc.
- **Layout components**: `src/components/layout/` — Header, Footer, etc.
- **Styles**: `src/styles/globals.css` — CSS custom properties (design tokens)
- **Utils**: `src/utils/` — cn, helpers

---

## 2. Color Usage — CRITICAL

**Never use arbitrary inline colors** (`bg-[#27E5EF]`, `text-[#18181b]`, `border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]`, etc.).

**Always use semantic token-based utilities** that resolve to CSS variables or Tailwind theme colors:

| Use Case | ✅ Semantic Class | ❌ Forbidden |
|----------|-------------------|--------------|
| Page background | `bg-background` | `bg-[#fafafa]` |
| Surface | `bg-surface-1`, `bg-surface-2`, `bg-surface-dark-1` | `bg-[#f4f4f5]` |
| Primary color | `bg-primary-base`, `text-primary-base` | `text-[#27E5EF]` |
| Accent | `bg-accent-base`, `text-accent-base` | `bg-[#FFC000]` |
| Text | `text-text`, `text-text-muted`, `text-text-inverted-1` | `text-[#18181b]` |
| Borders | `border-border-base`, `border-border-divider` | `border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]` |
| Focus ring | `focus:outline focus:outline-2 focus:outline-focus-outline focus:outline-offset-2` | `focus:ring-[#206cdf]` |
| Overlays | `bg-overlay-backdrop`, `bg-overlay-uniform` | `bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.6)]` |

If a semantic utility does not exist for a token, add it to `tailwind.config.ts` first by mapping to a CSS variable in `globals.css`.

**Exception**: `src/styles/globals.css` and `src/tokens/colors.ts` define the raw hex/rgba values. These are the source of truth — only these files may contain raw color values. Components reference them via semantic Tailwind classes or CSS variables.

---

## 3. Design Tokens — Source of Truth

- **Colors**: `src/tokens/colors.ts` + `src/styles/globals.css` (`--color-*`)
- **Spacing**: `src/tokens/spacing.ts` + `--spacing-*` (use: 3px, 5px, 8px, 10px, 15px, 20px, 30px, 40px, 60px, 80px, 120px)
- **Typography**: `src/tokens/typography.ts` + `--font-sans`, `--font-mono`
- **Motion**: `src/tokens/motion.ts` + `--motion-*`, `--motion-easing-*`
- **Layout**: `src/tokens/layout.ts` — container 1200px, 12-col grid, gutters, margins

Use only the values defined in tokens. Do not introduce new values.

---

## 4. Layout & Grid

- **Container**: `max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-5` (or `max-w-container mx-auto px-container`)
- **Grid**: `grid grid-cols-12 gap-[15px]` (responsive per breakpoints)
- **Breakpoints**: xs (base), sm (640px), md (768px), lg (1024px), xl (1280px), 2xl (1536px)
- **Spacing**: Use `spacing-*` tokens — e.g. `p-spacing-md`, `gap-spacing-sm`

---

## 5. Typography

- **Sans (primary)**: Satoshi Variable — titles, headers, body
- **Mono**: Oxygen Mono — subtitles, UI labels, buttons
- Apply via `font-sans` and `font-mono` (Tailwind) or `.mono` utility class

---

## 6. Surfaces & Cards

- **Card**: `bg-surface-dark-1` (or card bg token), `border border-border-base`, `rounded-none`, padding `p-[15px]`
- **Border radius**: 4px or 8px only; cards use 0px (sharp edges)
- **Elevation**: No decorative box-shadow. Use 1px borders or background contrast.
- **Card layouts**: Cover, top-image, inset, horizontal — defined in design system

---

## 7. Motion

- **Micro (hover, focus)**: 60ms `cubic-bezier(0,.9,.1,1)`
- **Transitions**: `transition-all duration-[60ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(0,.9,.1,1)]`
- **Reduced motion**: Respect `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)` — disable or shorten animations

---

## 8. Components

- **Buttons**: Use `Button` from `src/components/ui/Button.tsx`. Variants: primary, secondary, ghost.
- **Cards**: Use `Card` from `src/components/ui/Card.tsx`. Variants: default, cover, top-image, inset, horizontal.
- **Icons**: Lucide React (`lucide-react`), 20px default, stroke-width 2.
- **Interactive states**: Implement hover, focus, active, disabled for all interactive elements.

---

## 9. Accessibility

- WCAG AA contrast; focus outlines 2px `#206cdf`; ARIA labels on icon-only buttons; keyboard navigation.
- Never remove focus styles without a visible replacement.

---

## 10. SEO & Performance

- Semantic HTML: `header`, `main`, `nav`, `article`, `footer`
- Metadata and Open Graph in layout/page files
- Static generation where possible; above-the-fold performance priority

---

## 11. Adding New Features

1. Add tokens to `src/tokens/` and `globals.css` if new values are needed
2. Extend Tailwind theme in `tailwind.config.ts` with semantic mappings to CSS vars
3. Build atomic components in `src/components/ui/` using only token-based classes
4. Compose layout components in `src/components/layout/`
5. Never add arbitrary hex/rgba values in className — always use semantic utilities
